                <p>Launch bookings started form mid July 2025, with a refundable ₹21,000 booking token. Pricing is expected between ₹25 30 lakh ex showroom, placing them in the premium affordable EV segment.</p>

                <p>The <span class="font-weight-700">VF 3</span>—a small, budget-friendly electric hatch—will follow in <span class="subheding">2026</span>, with an anticipated ex-showroom price around<span class="subheading"> ₹10 lakh</span> and a claimed range of ~215 km.</p>
