                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Dealerships:</span> VinFast has signed with 13 dealer groups to open 32 showrooms across 27<span class="font-weight-700"> Indian cities</span>, planning to expand to 35 showrooms by end of 2025. These include major EV hubs like Delhi, Mumbai, Bengaluru, Chennai, Hyderabad, Pune, Jaipur, Ahmedabad, and more.</li>
